GConsole

public GConsole()
Constructs a default GConsole. The tiles are set to 32x32 and the console is initially 20x20

GConsole

public GConsole(int tileSize,
                int width,
                int height,
                int tileSetSize)
Constructs a GConsole with the given size. The tileSize represents the size of each tile on the screen, while tileSetSize is the size of the tiles in the tiles sets used.
